{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0001", "text": "藍是越夜越靜越美麗 的一種氣氛", "structure": {"line_index": 1, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 5, 2, 3, 3, 9, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "jyut6", "je6", "jyut6", "zing6", "jyut6", "mei5", "lai6", "dik1", "jat1", "zung2", "hei3", "fan1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "越夜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "越靜越", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "美麗", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一種", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "氣氛", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": null, "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0002", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0002", "text": "藍是越妒越恨越快樂 的一種鬥爭", "structure": {"line_index": 2, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 2, 4, 2, 2, 2, 4, 2, 3, 3, 9, 4, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "jyut6", "dou3", "jyut6", "han6", "jyut6", "faai3", "lok6", "dik1", "jat1", "zung2", "dau3", "zang1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "越妒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "越", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "恨", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "越", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快樂", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一種", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "鬥爭", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0001", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0003", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0003", "text": "藍是如迷如幻卻很迫真的某種興奮", "structure": {"line_index": 3, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 2, 4, 9, 3, 3, 3, 5, 9, 3, 5], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "jyu4", "mai4", "jyu4", "waan6", "koek3", "han2", "baak1", "zan1", "dik1", "mau5", "zung2", "hing1", "fan5"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如迷", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "如幻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "卻", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "很迫", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "真的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "某種", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "興奮", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0002", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0004", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0004", "text": "只可意會沒法說 講不出的快感", "structure": {"line_index": 4, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [9, 9, 4, 2, 4, 4, 9, 3, 3, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["zi2", "ho2", "ji3", "mut6", "faat3", "syut3", "gong2", "bat1", "ceot1", "dik1", "faai3", "gam2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "只可意會", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "沒法", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "說", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "講不出", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "快感", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0003", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0005", "paragraph_id": "para_01"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0005", "text": "藍是輾轉反側在午夜 想起你睡也不穩", "structure": {"line_index": 5, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 9, 9, 9, 3, 2, 5, 2, 9, 9, 5, 2, 5, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "zin2", "zyun2", "faan2", "zak1", "zoi6", "ng5", "je6", "soeng2", "hei2", "nei5", "seoi6", "jaa5", "bat1", "wan2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "輾轉反側", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "在", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "午夜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "想起", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "睡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "也", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不穩", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0004", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0006", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0006", "text": "藍是盛着寂寞釀的酒 跟星星對飲", "structure": {"line_index": 6, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 0, 2, 2, 2, 2, 3, 9, 3, 3, 3, 4, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "sing4", "zoek6", "zik6", "mok6", "joeng6", "dik1", "zau2", "gan1", "sing1", "sing1", "deoi3", "jam2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "盛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "着", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "寂寞", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "釀", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "酒", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "星星", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對飲", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0005", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0007", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0007", "text": "藍是傳來流動怨曲聲音 跟你的聲線", "structure": {"line_index": 7, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3, 5, 3, 3, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "cyun4", "loi4", "lau4", "dung6", "jyun3", "kuk1", "sing1", "jam1", "gan1", "nei5", "dik1", "sing1", "sin3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "傳來", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "流動", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "怨曲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聲音", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "跟", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "聲線", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0006", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0008", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0008", "text": "甚相近 似幕調情戲 難掩蓋的風韻", "structure": {"line_index": 8, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [2, 2, 5, 2, 2, 0, 4, 0, 9, 4, 3, 3, 2], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["sam6", "gan6", "ci5", "mok6", "diu6", "cing4", "hei3", "naan4", "jim2", "goi3", "dik1", "fung1", "wan6"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "甚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "相近", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "似幕", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "調情", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "戲", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "難", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "掩蓋", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "風韻", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0007", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0009", "paragraph_id": "para_02"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0009", "text": "我不清楚根本天生喜歡那樣藍", "structure": {"line_index": 9, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [5, 3, 3, 9, 3, 9, 3, 3, 9, 3, 5, 2, 0], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["ngo5", "bat1", "cing1", "co2", "gan1", "bun2", "tin1", "sang1", "hei2", "fun1", "naa5", "joeng6", "laam4"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "清楚", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "根本", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天生", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "喜歡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "那樣", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "藍", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0008", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0010", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0010", "text": "還是我已對你這種色彩太習慣", "structure": {"line_index": 10, "char_count": 13}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 5, 5, 4, 5, 5, 9, 3, 9, 4, 2, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["waan4", "si6", "ngo5", "ji5", "deoi3", "nei5", "ze5", "zung2", "sik1", "coi2", "taai3", "zaap6", "gwaan3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "還是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "我", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "已", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "對", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "這種", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "色彩", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "太", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "習慣", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0009", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0011", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0011", "text": "世間繽紛風景好比煙花匆匆一剎 便吹散", "structure": {"line_index": 11, "char_count": 17}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 3, 3, 3, 9, 9, 9, 3, 3, 3, 3, 3, 4, 2, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["sai3", "ban1", "fan1", "fung1", "ging2", "hou2", "bei2", "jin1", "faa1", "cung1", "cung1", "jat1", "caat3", "bin6", "ceoi1", "saan2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "世間", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "繽紛", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "風景", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "好比", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "煙花", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "匆匆", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一剎", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "便", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "吹散", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0010", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0012", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0012", "text": "看盡濃和淡 還只有它不散", "structure": {"line_index": 12, "char_count": 11}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [4, 2, 0, 0, 2, 0, 9, 5, 3, 3, 9], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["hon3", "zeon6", "nung4", "wo4", "daam6", "waan4", "zi2", "jau5", "taa1", "bat1", "saan2"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "看盡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "濃和淡", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "還", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "只有", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "它", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "不散", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0011", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0013", "paragraph_id": "para_03"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0013", "text": "藍是將小小一幅天空 剪低了做你恤衫", "structure": {"line_index": 13, "char_count": 16}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 3, 9, 9, 3, 3, 3, 3, 9, 3, 5, 2, 5, 3, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "zoeng1", "siu2", "siu2", "jat1", "fuk1", "tin1", "hung1", "zin2", "dai1", "liu5", "zou6", "nei5", "seot1", "saam1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "將", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "小小", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "一幅", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "天空", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "剪低", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "了", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "做", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "你", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "恤衫", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0012", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0014", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0014", "text": "藍是鋪開夜夜浪接浪 海水色被單", "structure": {"line_index": 14, "char_count": 14}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 3, 3, 2, 2, 2, 4, 2, 9, 9, 3, 2, 3], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "pou1", "hoi1", "je6", "je6", "long6", "zip3", "long6", "hoi2", "seoi2", "sik1", "bei6", "daan1"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "鋪開", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "夜夜", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "浪接浪", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "海水", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "色", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "被單", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0013", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0015", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
{"id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0015", "text": "藍是纏綿完後歇息之間 悽美的感嘆", "structure": {"line_index": 15, "char_count": 15}, "semantics": {"themes": [], "sentiment": "neutral", "keywords": []}, "prosody": {"tone_pattern": [0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 2, 4, 3, 3, 3, 5, 3, 9, 4], "tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping": ["laam4", "si6", "cin4", "min4", "jyun4", "hau6", "hit3", "sik1", "zi1", "cai1", "mei5", "dik1", "gam2", "taan3"]}, "nlp": {"tokens": [{"text": "藍是", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "纏綿", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "完後", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "歇息", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "之間", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "悽美", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "的", "pos": "X"}, {"text": "感嘆", "pos": "X"}], "syntax_notes": ""}, "source": {"title": "有人喜歡藍", "artists": ["蘇永康"], "lyricists": ["黃偉文"], "year": 0, "genre": []}, "context_links": {"doc_id": "feitsui_744", "prev_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0014", "next_line_id": "lyr_6IuP5rC45bq3_NzQ0_0016", "paragraph_id": "para_04"}}
